General.Name: Aerison Group Ltd
General.Description: Aerison Group Limited operates as an engineering, design, and construction company in Australia. It operates in Construction Services and Asset Services segments. The company provides engineering and design, procurement, project management, manufacturing, fabrication, structural, mechanical, piping, electrical, instrumentation and controls, construction, mechanical installation, commissioning, and asset services. It also offers environmental solutions, such as dry and wet dust collection, greenhouse gas reduction, acoustic engineering, and water and wastewater treatment systems. The company serves the minerals and mining, oil and gas, infrastructure, and power generation industries. Aerison Group Limited was founded in 1988 and is headquartered in West Perth, Australia.
